    "body": "Hmm, while not ideal, this does work today:\n\n``` rust\nlet a;\nlet b = Some(1);\nmatch b {\n  Some(c) if {\n    a = c+1;\n    a == 2\n  } => println!(\"{}\", a),\n  Some(_) => println!(\"Some\"),\n  None => println!(\"None\")\n}\n```\n\nPrints `2`;\n",
